                        "ProjectMissionDescription": {
                            "val": "This program develops Battle Management and Command and Control (BMC2) applications for the Joint Task Force - Space Defense (JTF-SD)(component for the National Space Defense Center (NSDC)). This includes developing hardware and software prototypes to support JNET developed with the US Strategic Command Joint Emergent Operational Need (ST-0006) and will continue to contribute towards developing hardware and software for an Accelerated BMC2 capability. The JTF-SD (and NSDC) allows the national security space community to effectively respond to potential future space threat events and will have the capability to develop, test, and integrate new space system tactics, techniques and procedures (TTPs) in support of both DoD and Intelligence Community operations."
                        },
